commit.message:
travis to GitHub actions (#723)

* Add a filename argument to the download functions and use a temporary path during the tests

* Disable notebook testing by default and only enable it via env variable

* Make it easier to summarize coverage results

* Update the requirements

Newer dask and distributed are needed for the bindings
Newer pandas is needed for some notebooks

This was the case since long, but it was unseen as travis did not send
notifications correctly.

* Replace travis file with github workflow files

* Move master to main
